title: BRIEF-Precio Fishbone Q3 EBITA up at SEK 2.7 million
text:

* Q3 net sales 39.8 million Swedish crowns ($4.7 million) versus 28.0 million crowns year ago
* Q3 EBITA 2.7 million crowns versus 1.5 million crowns year ago
